4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become an AI Machine Learning Engineer," which aims to help individuals start a career in data science and build their first ML models. The course duration is 16 weeks, with three classes held weekly. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. No previous experience is required, and the course is available in both English and Spanish. The instructors for this course are Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena, each with extensive experience in the field of AI and machine learning. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and various machine learning algorithms. Students will also have the opportunity to work on real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. Upon completion, participants will receive certificates recognized by multiple organizations. For more information, visit their website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning).

